Occurrence records for the species Amblyomma americanum

Source: R/occ_doc.R
occ_train.Rd

A dataset containing geographic coordinates of a North American tick.

occ_train

Format

A data frame with 89 rows and 3 columns.

Species

character, species scientific name.

Longitude

numeric, longitude values.

Latitude

numeric, latitude values.

Source

https://www.gbif.org/

Examples

data("occ_train", package = "rangemap")
head(occ_train)

#>                Species Longitude Latitude
#> 1 Amblyomma_americanum -83.55521 41.66394
#> 2 Amblyomma_americanum -81.62371 34.71541
#> 3 Amblyomma_americanum -76.28024 36.70818
#> 4 Amblyomma_americanum -87.99528 35.38694
#> 5 Amblyomma_americanum -94.17794 35.26075
#> 6 Amblyomma_americanum -88.03589 36.74891
